 8→
 9→/**
10→ * DO NOT USE THIS COMPONENT DIRECTLY INSTEAD USE `ErrorBoundary`.
11→ *
12→ * `DefaultErrorBoundary` is a generic Error Boundary component. This component is used in development builds.
13→ * @param param0 - The props
14→ * @param param0.children - The children
15→ * @param param0.homeURL - The home URL of the application.
16→ * @returns - The wrapped component.
